  <brief_title>Efficacy of Peg-interferon α-2a in Hepatitis B Patients Treated by Entecavir Without HBeAg Loss</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Efficacy of Peg-interferon α-2a in HBeAg (+) Chronic Hepatitis B Patients Who Have Been Treated by Entecavir for 48 Weeks But Without HBeAg Loss</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
